1
00:00:14,938 --> 00:00:16,977
Mr. Ye, you know

2
00:00:16,977 --> 00:00:18,278
our company's situation.

3
00:00:18,898 --> 00:00:21,677
The Chenghai order is our last hope.

4
00:00:22,258 --> 00:00:24,537
I understand your difficulties,

5
00:00:24,838 --> 00:00:27,118
but Chenghai is not a charity.

6
00:00:27,377 --> 00:00:30,738
I need to consider such a big risk carefully.

7
00:00:37,918 --> 00:00:39,977
Mr. Ye, could you reconsider?

8
00:01:21,577 --> 00:01:27,217
Do you like it? Maybe I can help you.

9
00:01:50,798 --> 00:01:53,057
Mr. Wu's leg function can be restored

10
00:01:53,057 --> 00:01:54,937
to normal walking level through rehabilitation,

11
00:01:55,197 --> 00:01:58,437
but nerve damage is irreversible.

12
00:01:58,997 --> 00:02:01,417
This means he can't

13
00:02:01,417 --> 00:02:03,458
can't run or jump anymore,

14
00:02:03,458 --> 00:02:04,937
or do any intense activities.

15
00:02:05,538 --> 00:02:06,417
Thank you.

16
00:02:16,678 --> 00:02:17,717
Isn't that a good thing?

17
00:02:18,077 --> 00:02:19,298
Then I'll be your

18
00:02:20,098 --> 00:02:22,217
personal slow driver.

19
00:02:25,178 --> 00:02:26,497
I'll make sure to take it one step at a time.

20
00:02:27,138 --> 00:02:29,937
I'll go wherever you want, safely.

21
00:02:32,418 --> 00:02:34,717
Where have you been these past few months?

22
00:02:35,738 --> 00:02:36,978
How did you get hurt?

23
00:02:37,217 --> 00:02:38,518
And why didn't you contact me?

24
00:02:39,898 --> 00:02:41,717
I was held captive by a group.

25
00:02:42,638 --> 00:02:44,597
I don't know who they are,

26
00:02:44,958 --> 00:02:46,877
nor why they did this.

27
00:02:48,777 --> 00:02:50,277
But who am I?

28
00:02:50,277 --> 00:02:52,097
I escaped successfully, didn't I?

29
00:02:55,257 --> 00:02:57,877
The diving accident wasn't an accident.

30
00:02:59,018 --> 00:03:02,178
They wanted to hurt me and got you involved.

31
00:03:02,798 --> 00:03:05,597
Those bastards. Were you injured?

32
00:03:08,018 --> 00:03:08,377
No.

33
00:03:10,377 --> 00:03:11,377
I'm glad

34
00:03:11,377 --> 00:03:12,777
it happened to me, not you.

35
00:03:13,518 --> 00:03:14,317
If it happened to you,

36
00:03:14,898 --> 00:03:16,317
what's the point of me coming back?

37
00:03:24,337 --> 00:03:26,118
The only thing that kept me going

38
00:03:26,978 --> 00:03:28,958
was the thought of seeing you again.

39
00:03:30,497 --> 00:03:31,377
Zhimei,

40
00:03:34,837 --> 00:03:37,837
we'll never be apart again,

41
00:03:39,118 --> 00:03:40,118
okay?

42
00:04:06,398 --> 00:04:07,638
Ma'am, I'm sorry.

43
00:04:17,958 --> 00:04:18,937
Just throw it away.

44
00:04:29,978 --> 00:04:32,197
He has to disappear from my life.

45
00:05:12,978 --> 00:05:13,778
Wu Xi is back.

46
00:05:14,997 --> 00:05:15,478
This family

47
00:05:17,418 --> 00:05:19,057
has nothing to do with you.

48
00:05:59,338 --> 00:06:00,278
No matter how well you pretend

49
00:06:01,197 --> 00:06:02,798
no matter how you pretend,

50
00:06:04,118 --> 00:06:05,218
you are not his.

51
00:06:05,778 --> 00:06:07,098
A person who has been missing for three months

52
00:06:07,397 --> 00:06:09,118
suddenly came back, don't you find it strange?

53
00:06:11,118 --> 00:06:12,897
Who is the biggest beneficiary of that accident?

54
00:06:13,118 --> 00:06:14,338
Have you ever thought about it?

55
00:06:15,437 --> 00:06:16,358
Zhimei,

56
00:06:16,978 --> 00:06:18,457
the person who hurt you hasn't been found yet.

57
00:06:18,457 --> 00:06:19,778
You can't trust anyone,

58
00:06:19,778 --> 00:06:20,757
including Wu Xi.

59
00:06:20,757 --> 00:06:21,918
What gives you the right to say that?

60
00:06:22,858 --> 00:06:25,118
You're the one who has been lying to me, aren't you?

61
00:06:41,118 --> 00:06:42,038
From now on,

62
00:06:44,118 --> 00:06:45,437
our paths don't cross.

63
00:07:29,538 --> 00:07:30,218
Zhimei.

64
00:07:30,437 --> 00:07:33,137
Why is there a new ring at home?

65
00:07:36,197 --> 00:07:38,778
I bought it because I like it.

66
00:07:40,338 --> 00:07:41,618
Sometimes,

67
00:07:41,957 --> 00:07:43,158
people do things

68
00:07:43,158 --> 00:07:43,897
they don't even know

69
00:07:43,897 --> 00:07:44,637
why they do.

70
00:07:45,957 --> 00:07:46,218
Yeah.

71
00:07:47,697 --> 00:07:50,118
Keep it if you like it.

72
00:08:46,657 --> 00:08:48,598
You can go now.

73
00:08:48,598 --> 00:08:50,037
No matter what you came for,

74
00:08:51,458 --> 00:08:53,157
it's all over.

75
00:09:45,838 --> 00:09:48,098
We can't be together anymore.

76
00:09:57,182 --> 00:09:57,903
Wu Xi.

77
00:09:58,223 --> 00:09:59,422
You met your wife.

78
00:10:00,662 --> 00:10:01,822
Am I right?

79
00:10:02,383 --> 00:10:03,322
Without you,

80
00:10:03,322 --> 00:10:04,422
she's still doing well.

81
00:10:04,422 --> 00:10:05,223
Listen,

82
00:10:05,643 --> 00:10:07,103
no matter what tricks you play,

83
00:10:07,863 --> 00:10:09,422
I won't let you hurt her again.

84
00:10:10,302 --> 00:10:11,623
With your current situation,

85
00:10:12,062 --> 00:10:13,562
you can't even take care of yourself.

86
00:10:13,903 --> 00:10:15,062
How can you protect her?

87
00:10:15,062 --> 00:10:16,202
Come on.

88
00:10:17,903 --> 00:10:19,462
Even if I have to give up my life,

89
00:10:20,483 --> 00:10:22,483
I will accompany you to the end.
